original_title: Five Year Diary, Reel 47: I Thought the Film Would End (October 21–November 2, 1986)
overview: The would-be penultimate Diary reel. Anne ruminates about the upcoming end of the Diary – and mourns it, of course. Familiar themes of Dr Who, drinking, comedy, and a nice trick-or-treat Halloween sequence. (Liz Coffey)
title: Five Year Diary, Reel 47: I Thought the Film Would End (October 21–November 2, 1986)
